                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Poor, careless</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                        <date>19 century</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ም፡/ምል፡/ምልጣ፡ for ምልጣን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Title of Text I; names of sections followed by the
                           name of the category of melody and/or by feast names (e.g., zǝmmāre
                           za-sanbata ʾayhud, zǝmmāre za-masqal); names of subsections (ṣǝwwaʿ,
                           Manfas); names of <term key="Qene" ana="#Qene">qǝne</term> (<term key="EtanaMogar" ana="#EtanaMogar">ʿǝṭāna mogar</term>) and antiphones (mawāśǝʾt, mǝlṭān);
                           names of versicles which are to be repeated and their abbreviations
                           (e.g., ብእሲ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ቅዱሱ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር and its abbrev. ብ, fols. 3vb-4ra); musical
                           notation signs: interlinear (e.g., fols. 5va-6ra, 7rab, 9ra, 12rab) and
                           elements of marginal signs; Ethiopic numerals.
 A few groups of lines
                           on the incipit page of Text I (fol. 29r).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">The handwriting changes in the course
                        of the text. On <locus from="16ra" to="16vb">16ra-16vb</locus> the letters
                        are big. On <locus target="#17ra">17ra</locus> the letters are slightly
                        bigger than before <locus target="#16ra">16ra</locus>.</handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- Tämälläs-sign, in the shape of two perpendicular lines, indicating the place where the omission written in the upper magin, belongs: <locus target="#27v">fol.  27v</locus> l.16. </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc>Omitted words and passages are written in the upper margin: fols. 2ra, 6rab, 20vb, 26r. </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc> Spaces for rubrication are left unfilled on fols. 13vb-16ra, 16vb-17rb, 20vb-21vb.</desc></item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
